---
import { Link } from '~/components/common';
import { BaseLayout } from '~/components/layout';
import { contacts } from '~/lib/data';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Abdul Malik"
  subtitle="(/Frən(t) ˈɛnd wɛb dɪˈvɛləpə/)."
  seo={{ title: 'Home' }}
>
  <section class="flex flex-col gap-5">
    <p>
      👋 Hello fellas, welcome to my digital garden ツ. I am Abdul, a software
      developer based in Bandung, Indonesia 🇮🇩, who specializes in Frontend Web
      Development. I am currently an active informatics student, full-time
      worker as a Frontend Web Developerat at a company in Bandung , and a
      part-time worker as an External Code Reviewer at
      <Link href="https://dicoding.com" ariaLabel="Dicoding Indonesia" isNewTab>
        Dicoding Indonesia
      </Link>.
    </p>

    <p>
      🎨 I focus on crafting user-friendly, accessible, and visually stunning
      websites. I casually work with the React ecosystem, mostly my tech stack
      is React, Vite/Next.js, Tailwind, and TypeScript. Currently, I learning
      about Vue too.
    </p>

    <p>
      ✍️ Recently, I've embarked on a journey into the world of writing. It's a
      new things that I love to do, and I am excited to share my writings. Check
      this out <Link href="/writings" ariaLabel="Writings page">here!</Link>.
    </p>

    <p>🌐 That's it, let's get in touch with me through my links below.</p>

    <ul class="text-sm grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
      {
        contacts.map((contact) => (
          <li>
            <Link href={contact.url} ariaLabel={contact.name} isNewTab>
              {contact.name}
            </Link>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
